## Navigation Flows

### Discovery Flow
```
DiscoveryScreen
├── WikiDetailScreen (push)
├── PostDetailScreen (push)
│   └── CreatorProfileScreen (push)
└── CreatorProfileScreen (push)
    └── PlanDetailScreen (push, future)
```

### Plan Flow
```
PlanScreen
├── GearDetailScreen (push, future)
├── ImportPlansScreen (push, future)
└── SharePlanSheet (modal bottom sheet)
```

### Camp Log Flow
```
CampLogScreen
├── CreateLogScreen (push or modal)
├── LogDetailScreen (push)
└── CreateVlogScreen (push, future)
```

### Community Flow
```
CommunityScreen
├── CircleDetailScreen (push, future)
└── ChatHistoryScreen (push, future)
```

### Profile Flow
```
ProfileScreen
├── EditProfileScreen (push, future)
├── SavedPlansScreen (push)
└── GearBoxScreen (push)
```

